::Skulletron::

	"Hmm.  Not bad.  Not bad at all.  Thank you Bloodystrike.  I'll remain
here, so if anyone needs me, they know where to find me!" Skulletron said
as he closed the door, but stopped halfway.  

	"By the way, let Zardus know that I am forever grateful to him for letting
me serve the Alliance," Skulletron shouted and shut the door completely
this time.
	
	Skulletron sat down in a chair and put his feet up on the control board.

	"For We Are Many," He said with a smile.
